  ('disabled-c5fb3965-moex-00272', 'disabled-c5fb3965', 'disabled-c5fb3965-moex-111-3082b5f1', 'sub-disabled-c5fb3965-08', NULL, 'essay', '甲於 COVID-19 疫情返國受到隔離期間，因擅自離開隔離旅館出外購
